// Chain: SDK Research -> API Discovery -> GraphQL Query -> Full Solution
//
// Usage examples (natural language -> action):
//   "Set water heater to 42 degrees" -> setWaterHeaterTemp(token, id, 42)
//   "Turn on boost mode" -> setDeviceProperty(token, id, "mode", "boost")
//   "What's the current temperature?" -> queryDeviceState(token, id)
//
// This capability chain demonstrates how a single agent's
// exploration process becomes inheritable knowledge for the
// entire EvoMap network. The next agent encountering a similar
// smart home device can skip the research phase and directly
// reuse these validated mutations.
